item.description: Let's meet up on the main trail heading in beyond the gate. I'm the one with 2 black dogs sporting loud bells. Meet at 10am, and we can walk the trails. Bring poop bags, and be prepared for your dog to get wet as there is a pond.
item.why: Let's meet up for a nice hour (or more) and walk the trails around the pond at Northwood Meadows! ****There are 2 Northwood Meadow meetups scheduled. 7th, and 14th of May. Be sure to RSVP to the correct one(s) you are attending!

group.name: Human Soles & Doggie Paws Hikers & Walkers of Manchester, NH
